snippet.title: Bravery and Greed -  Online Multiplayer Playthrough
snippet.description:
A live session we have recorded to showcase the online multiplayer feature. Still some tweaks to make and we got lucky with the loot, but we hope you will enjoy our run!

Subscribe to our newsletter to be notified about the release of the game/demo!
https://goo.gl/forms/WOHbb5iRZkM4dOkE3

Visit http://braveryandgreed.com/ for more info about the game!
